name: BMO Tactical Dividend ETF Fund
longDescription: This funds objective is to provide long term capital growth and current income by investing primarily in a diversified portfolio of exchange traded funds that invest in income producing securities. The funds asset mix may be changed over time to reflect the portfolio managers outlook for each asset class.
